  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Liars Dice is a bluffing-based roguelike about hidden dice, bold wagers, and outsmarting your opponents through deception and deduction.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/a6360d44e3efc4bf8c0fb132932906b2.poster.avif?t=1767484748\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/a6360d44e3efc4bf8c0fb132932906b2.webm?t=1767484748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/a6360d44e3efc4bf8c0fb132932906b2.mp4?t=1767484748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Deceive to Survive</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Outsmart, out bluff, and outlast to win your freedom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/888dc5681bc7c26b6548cd31441da8a5.poster.avif?t=1767484748\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/888dc5681bc7c26b6548cd31441da8a5.webm?t=1767484748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/888dc5681bc7c26b6548cd31441da8a5.mp4?t=1767484748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Roll for Survival</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each roll is a gamble, every round a mind game. Will your instincts guide you to victory?                                          <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/5eb47a5831d5136f7213945eb15d0a1f.poster.avif?t=1767484748\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/5eb47a5831d5136f7213945eb15d0a1f.webm?t=1767484748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/5eb47a5831d5136f7213945eb15d0a1f.mp4?t=1767484748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Duel of Destiny </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two players, twelve dice, and one dark truth: only one will make it out alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/8d9764787b16311d7d02e6f552d3b3c1.poster.avif?t=1767484748\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/8d9764787b16311d7d02e6f552d3b3c1.webm?t=1767484748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/8d9764787b16311d7d02e6f552d3b3c1.mp4?t=1767484748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Survive the Shadows</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you be the one who survives, or will the darkness claim you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/e5fa581105ae57f4f3a3f81d9962fed0.poster.avif?t=1767484748\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/e5fa581105ae57f4f3a3f81d9962fed0.webm?t=1767484748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/e5fa581105ae57f4f3a3f81d9962fed0.mp4?t=1767484748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
