ared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/5eb47a5831d5136f7213945eb15d0a1f.poster.avif?t=1767484748\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/5eb47a5831d5136f7213945eb15d0a1f.webm?t=1767484748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/5eb47a5831d5136f7213945eb15d0a1f.mp4?t=1767484748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Duel of Destiny </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two players, twelve dice, and one dark truth: only one will make it out alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/8d9764787b16311d7d02e6f552d3b3c1.poster.avif?t=1767484748\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/8d9764787b16311d7d02e6f552d3b3c1.webm?t=1767484748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/8d9764787b16311d7d02e6f552d3b3c1.mp4?t=1767484748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Survive the Shadows</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you be the one who survives, or will the darkness claim you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/e5fa581105ae57f4f3a3f81d9962fed0.poster.avif?t=1767484748\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274940/extras/e5fa581105ae57f4f3a3f81d9962fed0.webm?t=1767484748\" type=\"video/webm; codec